</p><p> Deftones 的其他夏季巡演日期包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">Primavera Sound Porto</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-werchter-2025-iggy-pop-underworld-and-gracie-abrams-lead-new-line-up-additions-3819822">Rock Werchter</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-2025-olivia-rodrigo-deftones-jamie-xx-more-buy-tickets-3816741">Roskilde</a> 。</p><p>该乐队是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gary-barlow-announces-songbook-2025-uk-ireland-tour-buy-tickets-3815502">Gary Barlow</a> （6 月 18 日）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-script">The Script</a> （25 场）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madness-to-headline-2025-eden-sessions-as-part-of-uk-summer-tour-3820164">Madness</a> （7 月 12 日）之后宣布参加 2025 年 Eden Sessions 的第四个乐队。据组织者称，更多的艺术家很快就会加入到名单中。</p><p>与此同时，哈利法克斯的 Piece Hall 也确认了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezer-announce-only-uk-headline-show-of-2025-with-bad-nerves-and-more-3812077">Weezer</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/khruangbin-announce-biggest-headline-show-gunnersbury-park-tv-on-the-radio-buy-tickets-3800167">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">The Libertines</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-travis-echo-the-bunnymen-faithless-halifax-summer-2025-headline-shows-3815599">Faithless</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulum-announce-two-massive-uk-headline-shows-for-2025-3813687">Pendulum</a>等乐队在明年的演出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chino Moreno 谈 Deftones 的遗产和未来" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IZwAURQsbyk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 2023 年 9 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deftones-tease-new-album-for-2024-3502767">Deftones 预告了一张即将推出的完整专辑（可能计划于 2024 年发行</a>），该专辑将继 2020 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/deftones-ohms-review-2758739">《Ohms》</a>之后。吉他手斯蒂芬·卡彭特当时表示，该乐队“开始为新唱片制作新材料”。</p><p>今年四月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deftones-give-update-on-a-new-album-we-have-a-whole-record-3617612">Deftones 向粉丝们通报了即将推出的完整项目的最新情况</a>。 “[我们]有一张完整的音乐唱片，”莫雷诺解释道。 “现在我的工作就是完成人声。”</p><p>但这位歌手表示，他不想为专辑的发行“设定明确的时间表”，并补充道：“我们并不着急。我们希望它很棒。我认为这是最重要的。但它即将到来，而且，是的——这真的很棒。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deftones-add-two-huge-shows-to-summer-2025-uk-tour-plans-buy-tickets-3820761">Deftones 为 2025 年夏季英国巡演计划增加两场大型演出的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
为了回应任天堂的法律诉讼，“Palworld”删除了受“口袋妖怪”启发的功能https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-removes-pokemon-inspired-feature-in-response-to-nintendo-legal-battle-382070 2?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=palworld-removes-pokemon-inspired-feature-in-response-nintendo-legal-battleIssy van der Velde Tue, 10 Dec 2024 10:51:37 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3820702 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Palworld：可以看到朋友正在使用攻击" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>没有给出改变的原因</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-removes-pokemon-inspired-feature-in-response-to-nintendo-legal-battle-3820702">为了回应任天堂的法律诉讼，“Palworld”删除了受“口袋妖怪”启发的功能，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Palworld：可以看到朋友正在使用攻击" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-dedicated-server-guide-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/palworld">Palworld</a></em>在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nintendo">任天堂</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/pokemon-is-suing-palworld-for-copyright-infringement-3795078">涉嫌专利侵权的</a>法律诉讼中改变了其核心机制之一。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/indiana-jones-great-circle-voice-actor-troy-baker-3818632">扮演印第安纳·琼斯是如何差点让特洛伊·贝克崩溃的</a></strong></li></ul><p>正如<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/palworld-ditches-pokeball-style-summoning-mechanic-amid-nintendo-legal-battle" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Eurogamer</em></a>所发现的那样，最近的<em>Palworld</em>更新取消了玩家用 Pal 球体召唤捕获的好友的功能，这些物品在投掷时会召唤其中的好友到达撞击点。任天堂声称<em>Palworld</em>侵犯的专利之一是能够向特定方向投掷物体以捕获生物或召唤战斗伙伴的能力。</p><p>现在，当玩家在游戏中召唤好友时，他们的化身会在他们面前举起一个球体，并在他们旁边召唤一个好友，而不是扔出球体并让好友出现在那里。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Palworld - 发布预告片 | PS5游戏" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ipy3ZazeEVg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1623730/view/4477236636060484669?l=english" target="_blank" rel="noopener">更新</a>说明中，没有给出更改的原因。 <em>NME</em>已联系 Pocket Pair 征求意见。</p><p> <em>Palworld</em>长期以来一直被称为<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/palworld-a-tale-of-adorable-monsters-friends-late-stage-capitalism-labour-exploitation-2985030">带枪的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/palworld-a-tale-of-adorable-monsters-friends-late-stage-capitalism-labour-exploitation-2985030"><em>口袋妖怪</em></a>，因为它包含可爱的小动物，你可以将它们抓成球并用来与你并肩作战。它以其基地建设机制和更暴力的基调而与众不同，但在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/the-pokemon-company-promises-to-investigate-palworld-over-ip-infringement-3576831">口袋妖怪公司承诺“调查”</a>这款游戏后，任天堂仍然起诉开发商 Pocket Pair 涉嫌侵犯版权。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-responds-to-truly-unfortunate-nintendo-lawsuit-3795221">Pocket Pair 对诉讼作出回应</a>，称其“不知道”自己涉嫌侵犯了哪些专利，并将采取“适当的法律诉讼”。</p><p>其声明中写道：“由于这起诉讼，我们将被迫分配大量时间来处理与游戏开发无关的事务，这确实很不幸。然而，我们将竭尽全力为我们的粉丝服务，并确保独立游戏开发者在追求他们的创意时不会受到阻碍或气馁。对于此消息引起的任何担忧或不适，我们向我们的粉丝和支持者表示歉意。”</p><p>其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/japanese-hip-hop-crew-don-yasa-release-hotline-miami-inspired-game-3820377">日本嘻哈乐队 Don Yasa 发布了一款<em>受迈阿密热线</em>启发的动作游戏</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-removes-pokemon-inspired-feature-in-response-to-nintendo-legal-battle-3820702">为了回应任天堂的法律诉讼，“Palworld”删除了受“口袋妖怪”启发的功能，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
